content: wtfsayo: This week, wtfsayo focused on implementing a new Jobs API for one-off agent messaging in the `elizaos/eliza` repository, merging a significant feature PR (#6098) that added over 5,300 lines of code. They also updated dependencies in the `elizaos-plugins/plugin-mcp` repository (#18) and have two additional PRs open to extend the new Jobs API. Their work was primarily concentrated on feature development, bugfixes, and refactoring across code, tests, and documentation.
